Welcome to the {{ group.name }}!

Everyone who is involved in the {{ group.name }} is expected to behave in accordance with the W3C Code of Ethics and Professional Conduct (CEPC):
  https://www.w3.org/Consortium/cepc/

You'll find information about the {{ group.name }} at:
  https://www.w3.org/groups/{{ shorttype }}/{{ group.shortname }}

If you have not already done so, link your GitHub account to your W3C account:
  https://www.w3.org/users/myprofile/connectedaccounts

We raise and discuss issues relating to {{ group.name }} itself on the WG repositories:
  https://www.w3.org/groups/{{ shorttype }}/{{ group.shortname }}/tools

For our meetings, check out our calendar at:
  https://auth.w3.org/?url=https://www.w3.org/groups/{{ shorttype }}/{{ group.shortname }}/calendar

If you have any questions or concerns, you can reach the {{ group.name }} chairs and team contacts 
(in Cc: of this message) directly.

